{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin</code></strong> 响应头指定了该响应的资源是否被允许与给定的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Origin\">origin</a>共享。</p>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Header type</th>\n      <th><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Response_header\">Response header</a></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Forbidden_header_name\">Forbidden header name</a></td>\n      <td>no</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *\nAccess-Control-Allow-Origin: &lt;origin&gt;\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"指令","title":"指令","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"sect1\">*</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>对于不需具备凭证（credentials）的请求，服务器会以“<code>*</code>”作为通配符，从而允许所有域都具有访问资源的权限。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"origin\">&lt;origin&gt;</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>指定一个可以访问资源的 URI。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>如需允许所有资源都可以访问<code>您</code>的资源，您可以如此设置：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *\n</pre></div>\n<p>如需允许<code>https://developer.mozilla.org</code>访问您的资源，您可以设置：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https://developer.mozilla.org\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cors_和缓存","title":"CORS 和缓存","isH3":true,"content":"<p>如果服务器未使用“<code>*</code>”，而是指定了一个域，那么为了向客户端表明服务器的返回会根据<code>Origin</code>请求头而有所不同，必须在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Vary\"><code>Vary</code></a>响应头中包含<code>Origin</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https://developer.mozilla.org\nVary: Origin\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#http-access-control-allow-origin","title":"Fetch Standard"}],"query":"http.headers.Access-Control-Allow-Origin"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"http.headers.Access-Control-Allow-Origin","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Allow-Origin/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Origin\"><code>Origin</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Vary\"><code>Vary</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"指令","id":"指令"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin 响应头指定了该响应的资源是否被允许与给定的origin共享。","popularity":0.0014,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/http/headers/access-control-allow-origin","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/http/headers/access-control-allow-origin/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://git